{"id":593,"date":"2008-03-10T10:47:46","date_gmt":"2008-03-10T15:47:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/boosting_boost.php"},"modified":"2008-03-10T10:47:46","modified_gmt":"2008-03-10T15:47:46","slug":"boosting_boost","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/boosting_boost.php","title":{"rendered":"Boosting Boost"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/archives\/boost_mobile_logo.gif\" alt=\"Boost Mobile Logo, Before and After\" \/><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.boostmobile.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Boost Mobile<\/a>, a &#8220;lifestyle-based telecommunications brand&#8221; and provider of mobile phones to the hip, the young and the restless has recently <a href=\"http:\/\/www.mobileburn.com\/pressrelease.jsp?Id=4222\">unveiled a new identity overhaul<\/a> &#8220;engineered&#8221; by the equally hip <a href=\"http:\/\/www.attik.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Attik<\/a>. The redesign includes the logo, of course, as well as a set of identity enhancements including new typefaces and colors in order to consistently brand the multitude of online and product offerings &mdash; from their <a href=\"http:\/\/www.boostmobilecommunity.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">online communities<\/a> to the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.boostmobilepro.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Boost Mobile Pro surfing competition<\/a>. Boost Mobile is clearly targeted towards a young consumer &mdash; their web site touts 4.3 million customers with the majority under the age of 25 and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.youtube.com\/results?search_query=boost+mobile&#038;search_type=\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">their TV ads are nothing short of head-scratchers<\/a> &mdash; so this redesign is spot on, especially in taking the original design and evolving it into a cleaner, bolder look. The icon feels a little more resolved to me, but I think the old one was pretty good too; and the typography is a definite improvement, as the old italicized version did not quite flow with the icon, and this one makes an interesting use of the letterfforms and creates with every character <em>kissing<\/em> each other &mdash; and, sure, it&#8217;s a little space agey, but it fits the brand and that&#8217;s what matters.<\/p>\n<p><span class=\"small\"><strong>Thanks to <a href=\"http:\/\/nicelogo.com\/BXC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Drew Dougherty<\/a> for the tip.<\/strong><\/small><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<img src=\"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/images\/excerpt_empty.gif\" alt=\"Excerpt Empty\" \/>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"episode_type":"","audio_file":"","duration":"","filesize":"","date_recorded":"","explicit":"","block":"","filesize_raw":""},"categories":[9,26,89],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/593"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=593"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/593\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=593"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=593"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.underconsideration.com\/brandnew\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=593"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}